---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy | Maple Leaf Corporation";
const description =
  "How Maple Leaf Corporation collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information across our website and ERP solutions.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-red-50 to-orange-50 pt-28 pb-12 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 md:mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        At Maple Leaf Corporation, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting
        the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we
        collect, use, store, and safeguard information when you visit our website or use our
        ERP, business management, and technology solutions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-3">We may collect the following information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Name, company name, and job title</li>
        <li>Email address and phone number</li>
        <li>Business information provided through contact forms</li>
        <li>Website usage data, including IP address, browser type, and device information</li>
        <li>Information voluntarily submitted through inquiries, consultations, or service requests</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-3">Maple Leaf Corporation uses collected information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
        <li>Provide ERP and business management solutions</li>
        <li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li>
        <li>Communicate product updates, service information, and business announcements</li>
        <li>Maintain security and prevent unauthorized access</li>
        <li>Comply with applicable legal requirements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your
        information against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or misuse. While we
        strive to protect your data, no method of online transmission is completely secure.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may use cookies and analytics tools to understand visitor behavior,
        improve performance, and enhance user experience. Users can manage cookie preferences
        through their browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We may use trusted third-party providers for website hosting, analytics,
        communication, and service delivery. These providers are required to handle
        information securely and only for authorized business purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        Maple Leaf Corporation does not sell, rent, or trade personal information. Information
        may only be disclosed when required by law or necessary to provide requested services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information by
        contacting us through the details provided on our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Industries We Serve</h2>
      <p>
        Our ERP and digital transformation solutions support organizations in manufacturing,
        distribution, wholesale, retail, trading, logistics, services, and other growing
        industries across Pakistan and international markets.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Policy Updates</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be published on this
        page with a revised effective date.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled,
        please <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium underline">contact Maple Leaf Corporation</a>
        through the contact information available on our website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
